] Yate B, Mostafa SM "Drug interaction?" Anaesthesia 39 (1984): 728-9[8] Chapple DJ, Clark JS, Hughes R "Interaction between atracurium and drugs used in anaesthesia." Br J Anaesth 55 Suppl 1 (1983): s17-22', 'Latanoprost, Apraclonidine, Neostigmine, Pilocarpine, Physostigmine, Acetylcholine, Bimatoprost, Travoprost, Brinzolamide, Brimonidine, Guanethidine, Levobunolol', 'Botulinum toxin type A', 1767369485);
